&lt;li&gt;3+ years experience working in business intelligence, data analytics, Data engineering or a similar role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong SQL skills and experience with data modeling techniques (e.g., dimensional modeling, 3 Nf, data vault)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in a programming language such as Python or Scala&lt;/li&gt;
