&lt;p&gt;You will lead a team of backend engineers responsible for the design and evolution of DoorDash’s Resolution Center platform. Your focus will be on building and scaling the systems that power Credits and Refunds, operational interventions, and resolution workflows across self-help, chatbot, voicebot, and agent-assisted channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will partner closely with Product, Machine Learning, Fraud, Data Science, and Strategy &amp;amp; Operations to define and deliver a roadmap that integrates ML-driven decisions, workflow orchestration, and strong configuration safeguards into high-volume production systems. This platform directly influences cost, fraud exposure, and customer trust. You will own the technical direction and operational excellence required to run it at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
