&lt;p&gt;Are you a dynamic and driven Accounting and Data professional ready to elevate your career? We have an exciting opportunity for a proactive and self-motivated individual with a strong command of US GAAP, revenue systems, and core data skills to join our growing Accounting team. This role offers the chance to showcase your expertise by collaborating with all levels of management and cross-functional teams, both internally and externally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll be at the forefront of cross-team collaboration, serving as the go-to expert for accounting partners in the data engineering and engineering spaces, creating a dynamic blend of responsibilities. Your days will be filled with reviewing data using SQL and Python, conducting in-depth data analysis and investigation, designing intricate drawings and flows, and contributing to groundbreaking accounting research and design requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us in this opportunity to not only apply your existing skills but also to cultivate new ones in a role that combines the best of both data engineering and accounting realms. Make your mark in a stimulating and remote-friendly environment where your expertise will be valued and your career can thrive.&lt;/p&gt;
